## How to Customize

### Adding Content
1.  **Open the HTML files** ([index.html](file:///C:/Users/akoda/.gemini/antigravity/brain/b3dc8f9a-8701-45a6-9bc0-a049d36ab941/index.html), etc.).
2.  **Find the placeholders**: Look for comments like `<!-- TEXT PLACEHOLDER -->` or text like `[Image Placeholder]`.
3.  **Replace them**: Insert your own text or `<img>` tags.

### Adding Links
- The sidebar has placeholder buttons for "About Me" and "Contact". You can update the `href="#"` to point to new pages you create.

